title: 2012 O'Neill Mutant Wetsuit
description: Accept no limitations. O'Neill's unique Modular Closure system makes the Mutant the most versatile wetsuit in our line. Now with an easier entry and new graphics. The Mutant is built with UltraFlex DS, UltraFlex Firewall and our all-new FluidFlex neoprene technology, making the Mutant warmer and more flexible than ever before. Two suits in one; now do some work son!
